Title: Absorption cross section and Hawking radiation in two-dimensional AdS

black holeAuthors: Won Tae Kim, John J. Oh, and Jung Hee Park

Comments: 6 pages, revtex, no figures

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D60 (1999) 047501

We calculate the absorption coefficient of scalar field on the background ofthe two-dimensional AdS black hole, which is of relevance to Hawking radiation.For the massless scalar field, we find that there does not exist any masslessradiation.